edit this post is mod approved so i did this last year on rfree where i made star maps for people to mark the special occasions of their lives and now that summer has started and i have some free time on my hands i would love to do that again on this subreddit since people here i figured might appreciate this offer more i do not really think i would need to define what a star map is over here but since i did that the last time i guess i might as well do it again so a star map really is a representation of the sky consisting of the constellations planets the moon and the sun as seen from a specific location during a given time
this makes it so that they are not only an excellent tool to guide us around the nightsky but they also make up for excellent souvenirs to treasure those specials moments of our lives
here are some examples of star maps these images are not mine 1 2 3 ill be making them for absolutely free
all you have to do is leave a comment and wait for me to get back to you via dms
i will eventually get back to everyone till i mark this post closed
 i am doing this only because last year when i did this on rfree i was completely overwhelmed by the reaction of people and how they sent me photos of them using the star maps as a dcor around their house it really made my summer also a few people decided to tip which i then used to buy courses on udemy would like to state that though that tips are no necessary
